### Submit a quick task (3 seconds default)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "generate-report"
}

### Submit a longer task (10 seconds)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "process-dataset",
  "duration": 10
}

### Submit a fast task (1 second)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "send-notification",
  "duration": 1
}

### Spawn multiple worker processes at once (each is an isolated actor)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "worker-alpha",
  "duration": 5
}

### Second worker process
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "worker-beta",
  "duration": 3
}

### Third worker process
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "worker-gamma",
  "duration": 7
}

### --- Error cases ---

### Missing name field
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "duration": 5
}

### Invalid JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

not-json

### Empty name
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "duration": 2
}
